thread.title: Shawn Mace

author: Shawn Mace
title: Shawn Mace
text: I ordered 4 trees from Willis Orchard spanning the past couple of years. Watered them almost every day throughout the warm months of the year. The trees are still alive and showing growth. Any time I had a question and called Willis Orchard with a question about my trees, How to plant, when to plant, I was given courteous service by knowledgeable professionals. This company stands by there warranty. My trees are still alive. To me, that speaks Quality.
